translated: Good of Burgundy, born in 1379 and died September 10, 1399 at age 20, is the daughter of the Duke of Burgundy Philip the Bold and Margaret III of Dampierre.
original: Bonne de Bourgogne, née en 1379 et morte le 10 septembre 1399 à 20 ans, est la fille du duc de Bourgogne Philippe le Hardi et de Marguerite III de Dampierre.
